   git --version    //to check version

 
   git config --global user.name “xxxx”
   git config --global user.name          //to check username

   git config --global user.email “xxxx”
   git config --global user.email          //to check email

   git config --global --list

 Create a demo project/folder  in local & add to git
  
   
Goto cmd OR terminal OR git bash 
     CD to the location of the folder and run following commands
   git init  //adding git
   git status
   git add .
   git commit -m “msg”
   git push -u “url” master

 
